---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Pre & Post-natal Women"
	description="Expert women's health physiotherapy through every stage of pregnancy and postnatal recovery."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Pre & Post-natal Women"
		breadcrumb="Pre & Post-natal Women"
	/>

	<ImageText
		image="/who-we-help/pregnant-gym.jpg"
		imageAlt="Pregnant woman smiling in the gym during a water break"
	>
		<p>Pregnancy and the postnatal period place extraordinary demands on the female body. At Balance, our women's health specialists provide expert knowledge and compassionate care at every stage, from early pregnancy through to long-term postnatal recovery.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/who-we-help/pregnant-stretching.jpg"
		imageAlt="Pregnant woman stretching her calves against a fence while training outdoors"
	>
		<p>Pelvic girdle pain, lower back pain, sciatica and postural changes are extremely common during pregnancy and all highly treatable. Our physiotherapists and osteopaths manage these conditions safely and effectively, keeping you as comfortable and active as possible throughout.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		image="/who-we-help/newborn-feet-in-hand.jpg"
		imageAlt="Newborn baby's feet cradled in a parent's hand"
	>
		<p>Pelvic floor health is central to our service. Whether preparing for birth, recovering from delivery or healing after a caesarean, our specialists provide thorough assessment and tailored rehabilitation. Pelvic floor dysfunction is far more common than many women realise and far more treatable. We provide a safe, private and non-judgmental space to address these concerns properly.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/who-we-help/newborn-feet-blanket.jpg"
		imageAlt="Newborn baby resting on a soft blanket"
	>
		<p>Postnatal recovery is about rebuilding strength, restoring energy and feeling like yourself again. Graduated exercise programmes, diastasis recti rehabilitation and return-to-sport guidance are all available, with our studios and gym accessible daily at your own pace.</p>
		<p>You deserve expert, joined-up care that supports not just your body, but your confidence and energy for life.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
